TODAY'S QUOTE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
"It's a miracle that nobody was seriously hurt. . . . I'm really surprised. The 
car didn't roll over, either. It just went down and landed on all four wheels." 
</P>
<P>
Compton Police Detective Michael Markey, speaking of an accident in which 14 
people in a single car survived a 70-foot plunge into a gravel pit. 
</P>
