<P>
LEGISLATION -- CALIFORNIA; COASTAL AREAS -- CALIFORNIA; OIL SPILLS -- 
CALIFORNIA; HAZARDOUS MATERIALS -- DISPOSAL; TANKERS; OIL INDUSTRY -- 
CALIFORNIA 
