PALESTINIANS -- ISRAEL; ISRAEL -- TERRITORIES AND POSSESSIONS; WEST BANK 
(ISRAEL); GAZA STRIP; ARABS -- ISRAEL; ISRAEL -- REVOLTS 
</P>
